document.full_text: world number one caroline wozniacki survived a stiff test from teenage serbian bojana jovanovski in the second round of the madrid open on tuesday, coming through 6-4 6-4 against the unseeded 19-year-old.
document.title: wozniacki tested by jovanovski at madrid open
